Surf_Pantheon by Garanimal
T1 Linear With 3 Bonuses and 3 Secrets
Bonus 1: Tier 2
Bonus 2: Tier 4
Bonus 3: Tier 3

A Note To Zoners: All endzones have been placed 2 units off of the 8 grid so as not to be cheated. You should be able to use the trigger multiples, which are on the 8 grid, for your endzones without any issues.
Intended for
sv_maxvelocity 10000     
sv_airaccelerate 150                
66 tick
This map is the final release of the original surf_pantheon_beta created for the Killzone Gaming surf mapping contest. I want to thank the mappers community for all of their help and support. I never would have finished this map without help from the Momentum and KSF discords.

I especially want to thank Bonjorno7 and Cabbage Mcgravel for their help with the models in this map. They did a fantastic job and I am very grateful to them for their hard work.

Thank you to my testers and thank you Juxtapo and Hesuka for the showcase!
